00:07:15.690 --> 00:07:17.010 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That was convenient.

00:07:17.010 --> 00:07:19.030 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: And so, he
had a private meeting

00:07:19.030 --> 00:07:21.660 align:middle line:84%
