his particular decorations,

00:07:28.940 --> 00:07:30.370 align:middle line:90%
his particular vision.

00:07:30.370 --> 00:07:34.080 align:middle line:84%
And at that time,
when I heard him speak

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:37.870 align:middle line:84%
