said that really got me,

00:07:37.870 --> 00:07:40.495 align:middle line:84%
I told Rickie, I
said, OK I'm in.

00:07:40.495 --> 00:07:41.370 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah, uh huh.

00:07:41.370 --> 00:07:42.670 align:middle line:90%
See, I remember that.

00:07:42.670 --> 00:07:44.350 align:middle line:90%
That was a very important time.

00:07:44.350 --> 00:07:46.450 align:middle line:84%
So we have a photo
of that, of you,

00:07:46.450 --> 00:07:49.660 align:middle line:84%
and that is your wife,
Rickie Byars Beckwith, who

00:07:49.660 --> 00:07:51.830 align:middle line:84%
