though our spiritual community

00:08:25.860 --> 00:08:28.340 align:middle line:10%
was so-called off
the beaten path,

00:08:28.340 --> 00:08:30.680 align:middle line:10%
once they came and
they heard the message,

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:34.260 align:middle line:10%
they felt the music,
they felt our desire

00:08:34.260 --> 00:08:35.860 align:middle line:10%
to make a difference
on the planet,

00:08:35.860 --> 00:08:37.390 align:middle line:10%
they got what we were about.

00:08:37.390 --> 00:08:40.100 align:middle line:10%
And we were highly endorsed
by some very powerful people.

00:08:40.100 --> 00:08:42.475 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And so you are making
