00:17:06.910 --> 00:17:11.640 align:middle line:84%
And an insight is an event that
takes place in consciousness,

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:13.579 align:middle line:84%
where suddenly you
are aware of something

00:17:13.579 --> 00:17:15.050 align:middle line:90%
you didn't know before.

00:17:15.050 --> 00:17:18.790 align:middle line:84%
And I say everyone
has that capacity.

00:17:18.790 --> 00:17:20.960 align:middle line:84%
The presence, whatever
name you want to call it,

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.150 align:middle line:90%
the Presence of God.

00:17:22.150 --> 00:17:25.220 align:middle line:84%
Love, Intelligence has
not made one mistake,

00:17:25.220 --> 00:17:27.829 align:middle line:84%
does not do do-overs,
does not repeat itself,

00:17:27.829 --> 00:17:30.840 align:middle line:84%
and everyone is fully
endowed with the capacity

00:17:30.840 --> 00:17:33.405 align:middle line:84%
to have insight, to allow
for their soul to evolve

00:17:33.405 --> 00:17:35.280 align:middle line:90%
and their oversoul to unfold.

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:37.350 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So though,
not necessarily

00:17:37.350 --> 00:17:40.450 align:middle line:84%
if you're in a place of
fear and survival so much,

00:17:40.450 --> 00:17:43.970 align:middle line:84%
is what do you hear
as the biggest angst

00:17:43.970 --> 00:17:45.990 align:middle line:84%
that people have in
your congregation?

00:17:45.990 --> 00:17:47.510 align:middle line:90%
That source of fear?

00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:50.042 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: Well, at
Agape they don't have any.

00:17:50.042 --> 00:17:52.690 align:middle line:90%
I'm kidding.

00:17:52.690 --> 00:17:57.150 align:middle line:84%
I think as it's a low-level
fear that people live from,

00:17:57.150 --> 00:18:01.650 align:middle line:84%
some of it's manufactured
by mass media.

00:18:01.650 --> 00:18:04.670 align:middle line:84%
There is a fear of
survive, a fear of dying,

00:18:04.670 --> 00:18:06.730 align:middle line:84%
a fear of lack,
loss, limitation.

00:18:06.730 --> 00:18:09.650 align:middle line:84%
It's a low-level fear that
people are hypnotized in.

00:18:09.650 --> 00:18:12.800 align:middle line:84%
You turn on corporate
media, and you'll

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:15.286 align:middle line:84%
notice there's always
something to be afraid of.

00:18:15.286 --> 00:18:17.910 align:middle line:84%
There's some new disease coming,
there's a terrorist happening,

00:18:17.910 --> 00:18:19.530 align:middle line:84%
there's always
something going on.

00:18:19.530 --> 00:18:20.812 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And that may be true.

00:18:20.812 --> 00:18:21.770 align:middle line:90%
I mean, those do exist.

00:18:21.770 --> 00:18:23.311 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: Yeah,
those things exist.

00:18:23.311 --> 00:18:25.840 align:middle line:84%
However, more
important than that,

00:18:25.840 --> 00:18:28.710 align:middle line:84%
the capacity within us to
deal with whatever issue

00:18:28.710 --> 00:18:32.080 align:middle line:84%
is bigger than what
we may be facing.

00:18:32.080 --> 00:18:35.380 align:middle line:84%
The power within us is
bigger than anything

00:18:35.380 --> 00:18:36.880 align:middle line:84%
that we may be
facing in the world.

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:38.830 align:middle line:84%
If there's a problem
in the world,

00:18:38.830 --> 00:18:41.210 align:middle line:84%
the answer has
already been created.

00:18:41.210 --> 00:18:42.990 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is
within us, but you

00:18:42.990 --> 00:18:44.660 align:middle line:90%
can't get to it through fear.

00:18:44.660 --> 00:18:47.940 align:middle line:84%
You can only get to it through
revelation and inspiration.

00:18:47.940 --> 00:18:50.720 align:middle line:84%
And so you have to
transcend the fear

00:18:50.720 --> 00:18:53.600 align:middle line:84%
or walk in the
direction of your faith

00:18:53.600 --> 00:18:56.582 align:middle line:84%
and take the fear with
you, until it translates,

00:18:56.582 --> 00:18:58.790 align:middle line:84%
transmutes itself into
excitement and then ultimately

00:18:58.790 --> 00:18:59.480 align:middle line:90%
enthusiasm.

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:01.310 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So whatever
we have inside of us

00:19:01.310 --> 00:19:03.090 align:middle line:84%
is much larger
than the fear that

00:19:03.090 --> 00:19:05.060 align:middle line:90%
is being touted to us all over.

00:19:05.060 --> 00:19:06.400 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Absolutely.

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:09.520 align:middle line:84%
And people see
themselves as victims.

00:19:09.520 --> 00:19:13.270 align:middle line:84%
They see themselves
as unresourceful.

00:19:13.270 --> 00:19:16.060 align:middle line:90%
They see themselves as lacking.

00:19:16.060 --> 00:19:20.770 align:middle line:84%
And holding that particular
vision of themselves,

00:19:20.770 --> 00:19:23.480 align:middle line:84%
they develop compulsive
behaviors, defense mechanisms,

00:19:23.480 --> 00:19:26.460 align:middle line:84%
and coping mechanisms to live
with that idea of themselves

00:19:26.460 --> 00:19:29.110 align:middle line:84%
and then try to go out
and make themselves happy.

00:19:29.110 --> 00:19:30.662 align:middle line:90%
It's not going to happen.

00:19:30.662 --> 00:19:32.370 align:middle line:84%
You have to change
your idea of yourself.

00:19:32.370 --> 00:19:34.440 align:middle line:84%
You have to catch
that you really

00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:39.640 align:middle line:84%
are a magnificent, luminous
being, full to overflowing

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:41.800 align:middle line:90%
with life and brilliance.

00:19:41.800 --> 00:19:44.204 align:middle line:84%
As you begin to fall
in love with that,

00:19:44.204 --> 00:19:45.370 align:middle line:90%
then something else happens.

00:19:45.370 --> 00:19:48.087 align:middle line:84%
You start to feel and hear
the guidance that's there.

00:19:48.087 --> 00:19:48.670 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:19:48.670 --> 00:19:49.885 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: But as you
used the word earlier,

00:19:49.885 --> 00:19:51.500 align:middle line:84%
there has to be a
vibrational match.

00:19:51.500 --> 00:19:54.350 align:middle line:84%
And so as you begin to
fall in love with yourself,

00:19:54.350 --> 00:19:56.190 align:middle line:84%
suddenly your intuition
starts to work.

00:19:56.190 --> 00:20:01.870 align:middle line:84%
You start to hear things, not
audibly, guidance, wisdom.

00:20:01.870 --> 00:20:05.250 align:middle line:84%
That starts to generate
the gifts within you,

00:20:05.250 --> 00:20:07.742 align:middle line:84%
and suddenly openings
are happening,

00:20:07.742 --> 00:20:09.200 align:middle line:84%
opportunities are
taking place, you

00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:11.980 align:middle line:84%
are meeting different
people, and suddenly

00:20:11.980 --> 00:20:15.230 align:middle line:84%
the issue that was so big,
an answer is showing up.

00:20:15.230 --> 00:20:16.480 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's how it happens.

00:20:16.480 --> 00:20:17.130 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Out of you.

00:20:17.130 --> 00:20:17.620 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:20:17.620 --> 00:20:20.203 align:middle line:84%
That is pretty much the formula
right there for how it happens

00:20:20.203 --> 00:20:22.200 align:middle line:84%
is you have to be the
vibrational match for it.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:23.158 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Absolutely.

