something was happening in me.

00:25:31.170 --> 00:25:34.160 align:middle line:84%
And I tried to shrink it
to make sure I was still--

00:25:34.160 --> 00:25:34.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Fit in.

00:25:34.840 --> 00:25:35.631 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Fit in.

