get back in the box again.

00:26:00.630 --> 00:26:01.320 align:middle line:90%
That was it.

00:26:01.320 --> 00:26:03.470 align:middle line:84%
The box shattered, and
the rest of my life

00:26:03.470 --> 00:26:07.450 align:middle line:84%
