00:34:46.900 --> 00:34:47.370 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's "Spiritual-- OK.

00:34:47.370 --> 00:34:48.260 align:middle line:90%
Got it.

00:34:48.260 --> 00:34:49.723 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Yeah.

00:34:49.723 --> 00:34:50.639 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's all good.

00:34:50.639 --> 00:34:51.639 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: It's a
lot of good work.

00:34:51.639 --> 00:34:51.810 align:middle line:90%
It

00:34:51.810 --> 00:34:53.060 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Is a lot of good work.

00:34:53.060 --> 00:34:53.719 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:34:53.719 --> 00:34:54.219 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:34:54.219 --> 00:34:55.530 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: But in the
life visioning process,

00:34:55.530 --> 00:34:57.430 align:middle line:84%
which is how I founded
Agape, I used the life

00:34:57.430 --> 00:34:58.760 align:middle line:90%
visioning process.

00:34:58.760 --> 00:35:03.440 align:middle line:84%
Basically, you establish a
field of unconditional love.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:06.140 align:middle line:90%
We've all tasted it to a degree.

00:35:06.140 --> 00:35:09.920 align:middle line:84%
Somebody's loved us
without any conditions.

00:35:09.920 --> 00:35:12.620 align:middle line:84%
Regardless of whatever condition
we were in, they loved us,

00:35:12.620 --> 00:35:13.710 align:middle line:90%
maybe a grandparent.

00:35:13.710 --> 00:35:16.220 align:middle line:90%
It may have been friend.

00:35:16.220 --> 00:35:18.240 align:middle line:84%
If we've never felt that,
we have to imagine it.

00:35:18.240 --> 00:35:20.650 align:middle line:84%
But we establish a field
of unconditional love.

00:35:20.650 --> 00:35:22.720 align:middle line:90%
And then, we ask a question.

00:35:22.720 --> 00:35:25.630 align:middle line:84%
What is God's idea of
itself as our life?

00:35:25.630 --> 00:35:29.590 align:middle line:84%
Or another way of asking it
is, what is it that within me

00:35:29.590 --> 00:35:32.492 align:middle line:84%
that's seeking to
emerge by means of me?

00:35:32.492 --> 00:35:34.450 align:middle line:84%
Now, the interesting
thing is that the universe

00:35:34.450 --> 00:35:36.410 align:middle line:84%
answers any questions
that you ask.

00:35:36.410 --> 00:35:40.004 align:middle line:10%
However, many people ask
disempowering questions.

00:35:40.004 --> 00:35:40.670 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Such as?

00:35:40.670 --> 00:35:42.030 align:middle line:10%
>>BECKWITH: Why me?

00:35:42.030 --> 00:35:43.210 align:middle line:10%
What's wrong?

00:35:43.210 --> 00:35:44.840 align:middle line:10%
Who's to blame?

00:35:44.840 --> 00:35:46.640 align:middle line:10%
People stay at that level.

00:35:46.640 --> 00:35:50.290 align:middle line:10%
But if you raise it
up and say, what's

00:35:50.290 --> 00:35:52.480 align:middle line:10%
trying to emerge through me?

00:35:52.480 --> 00:35:55.060 align:middle line:84%
You start to get
into intuitive hits

00:35:55.060 --> 00:35:58.450 align:middle line:84%
about your own soul
that's seeking to unfold.

00:35:58.450 --> 00:36:00.620 align:middle line:84%
So in the life
visioning process,

00:36:00.620 --> 00:36:03.850 align:middle line:84%
we learn how to ask that
question and be still enough

00:36:03.850 --> 00:36:05.860 align:middle line:84%
and develop the
listening capacity

00:36:05.860 --> 00:36:08.460 align:middle line:90%
to hear with the inner ear.

00:36:08.460 --> 00:36:10.950 align:middle line:84%
Then, once we're able
to articulate the vision

00:36:10.950 --> 00:36:14.520 align:middle line:84%
to a degree, that's
just stage one and two.

00:36:14.520 --> 00:36:17.090 align:middle line:84%
Third stage is, we
have to ask, what

00:36:17.090 --> 00:36:19.990 align:middle line:84%
is it that I must
become in order

00:36:19.990 --> 00:36:23.400 align:middle line:84%
to manifest the vision that
I'm now learning to articulate.

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:25.840 align:middle line:90%
Now, that's our growing edge.

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:28.790 align:middle line:84%
That means, we're starting to
see where we need to change,

00:36:28.790 --> 00:36:31.460 align:middle line:84%
where we need to take
personal self-responsibility

00:36:31.460 --> 00:36:32.780 align:middle line:90%
for our own life.

00:36:32.780 --> 00:36:34.630 align:middle line:90%
Habits we need to drop.

00:36:34.630 --> 00:36:36.690 align:middle line:90%
Habits we need to develop.

00:36:36.690 --> 00:36:37.820 align:middle line:90%
Gifts we need to cultivate.

00:36:37.820 --> 00:36:39.910 align:middle line:90%
Where must I grow?

00:36:39.910 --> 00:36:40.410 align:middle line:90%
You see?

00:36:40.410 --> 00:36:42.580 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Have you ever
noticed that people

00:36:42.580 --> 00:36:45.110 align:middle line:84%
come into the community,
and they act a certain way.

00:36:45.110 --> 00:36:45.920 align:middle line:90%
And they believe.

00:36:45.920 --> 00:36:48.810 align:middle line:84%
And they love the
messages, but there's

00:36:48.810 --> 00:36:51.410 align:middle line:84%
a disconnect when life
happens, when they go back

00:36:51.410 --> 00:36:53.180 align:middle line:90%
to the job and the stress.

00:36:53.180 --> 00:36:56.362 align:middle line:90%
How do you bridge that gap?

00:36:56.362 --> 00:36:58.070 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: It's like
an Olympic athlete.

00:36:58.070 --> 00:36:59.840 align:middle line:90%
You have to practice.

00:36:59.840 --> 00:37:01.860 align:middle line:84%
You don't just suddenly
one day wake up

00:37:01.860 --> 00:37:05.780 align:middle line:84%
and run the 100-yard
dash in under 10 seconds.

00:37:05.780 --> 00:37:09.250 align:middle line:84%
It's a day by day practice
that allows for the potential

00:37:09.250 --> 00:37:09.917 align:middle line:90%
to come forward.

00:37:09.917 --> 00:37:11.666 align:middle line:84%
Whether you're an
artist or whether you're

00:37:11.666 --> 00:37:13.380 align:middle line:84%
a singer, a piano
player, whatever it is,

00:37:13.380 --> 00:37:14.450 align:middle line:90%
you have to practice.

00:37:14.450 --> 00:37:16.140 align:middle line:90%
So you have the theory.

00:37:16.140 --> 00:37:17.300 align:middle line:90%
You have a belief.

00:37:17.300 --> 00:37:21.770 align:middle line:84%
Now, the belief is what I call
an operational placeholder

00:37:21.770 --> 00:37:23.342 align:middle line:90%
for practice and insight.

00:37:23.342 --> 00:37:25.050 align:middle line:84%
You believe that all
things are possible.

00:37:25.050 --> 00:37:27.160 align:middle line:84%
You believe there's
a vision within you.

00:37:27.160 --> 00:37:29.086 align:middle line:84%
But now, you have to
have a level of practice.

00:37:29.086 --> 00:37:30.460 align:middle line:84%
So a life visioning
process helps

00:37:30.460 --> 00:37:34.180 align:middle line:84%
you practice so
that you're provided

00:37:34.180 --> 00:37:37.050 align:middle line:90%
with ultimately an insight.

00:37:37.050 --> 00:37:39.840 align:middle line:84%
And then, you start to
embody that insight.

00:37:39.840 --> 00:37:41.650 align:middle line:90%
You start to grow.

00:37:41.650 --> 00:37:46.610 align:middle line:84%
So what happens is,
there's people that come.

00:37:46.610 --> 00:37:47.920 align:middle line:90%
And they get excited about it.

00:37:47.920 --> 00:37:49.750 align:middle line:84%
But when they realize
that you're not

00:37:49.750 --> 00:37:52.170 align:middle line:84%
going to ride to heaven on the
coattails of someone else--

00:37:52.170 --> 00:37:52.530 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:37:52.530 --> 00:37:52.890 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:37:52.890 --> 00:37:53.210 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:37:53.210 --> 00:37:55.085 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: And there's
not magical thinking.

00:37:55.085 --> 00:37:57.010 align:middle line:90%
It's not wishful thinking.

00:37:57.010 --> 00:37:59.710 align:middle line:84%
And you actually have
to do some inner work.

00:37:59.710 --> 00:38:02.030 align:middle line:84%
Then, there's a group
that drops off there.

00:38:02.030 --> 00:38:02.530 align:middle line:90%
And then--

00:38:02.530 --> 00:38:04.800 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You have to stop
the conversations also.

00:38:04.800 --> 00:38:05.510 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Yes.

00:38:05.510 --> 00:38:05.830 align:middle line:90%
The chatter.

00:38:05.830 --> 00:38:07.038 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: The negative chatter.

00:38:07.038 --> 00:38:08.850 align:middle line:84%
And the surrounding
yourself with people

00:38:08.850 --> 00:38:10.740 align:middle line:84%
that support the
negative chatter

00:38:10.740 --> 00:38:13.042 align:middle line:84%
and being a part of that
conversation as well.

00:38:13.042 --> 00:38:14.000 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Absolutely.

00:38:14.000 --> 00:38:16.870 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I notice that as
I grew spiritually that

00:38:16.870 --> 00:38:19.230 align:middle line:84%
my set of friends
completely changed.

00:38:19.230 --> 00:38:22.300 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: As you change,
the vibrational match changes.

00:38:22.300 --> 00:38:24.020 align:middle line:84%
So then you have
another group of people

00:38:24.020 --> 00:38:25.430 align:middle line:90%
that match who you are today.

00:38:25.430 --> 00:38:25.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:25.930 --> 00:38:26.500 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:38:26.500 --> 00:38:26.910 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Absolutely.

00:38:26.910 --> 00:38:27.451 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:38:27.451 --> 00:38:30.090 align:middle line:84%
And I realized that I was
a part of that conversation

00:38:30.090 --> 00:38:32.930 align:middle line:84%
in the past because that
was where I was resonating,

00:38:32.930 --> 00:38:35.087 align:middle line:90%
in complaint or in victimhood.

00:38:35.087 --> 00:38:36.670 align:middle line:84%
And that was the
poverty consciousness

00:38:36.670 --> 00:38:38.980 align:middle line:84%
I was creating within
my spirit at the time.

00:38:38.980 --> 00:38:41.180 align:middle line:84%
And of course,
that set of friends

00:38:41.180 --> 00:38:44.340 align:middle line:84%
was that vibrational match,
and as I grew spiritually,

00:38:44.340 --> 00:38:47.280 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't have this
conversation with those people.

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:50.390 align:middle line:84%
And it hurt because I was
losing friends and having

00:38:50.390 --> 00:38:51.250 align:middle line:90%
confrontations.

00:38:51.250 --> 00:38:52.540 align:middle line:90%
And it was uncomfortable.

00:38:52.540 --> 00:38:54.480 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: And that's
part of the messy birth

00:38:54.480 --> 00:38:55.660 align:middle line:90%
on an individual level.

00:38:55.660 --> 00:38:58.720 align:middle line:84%
What you're describing
there is the transformation

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:00.320 align:middle line:90%
takes place individually.

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:03.300 align:middle line:84%
So going back to your previous
question on the global sense,

00:39:03.300 --> 00:39:05.100 align:middle line:90%
that's what happens globally.

00:39:05.100 --> 00:39:08.890 align:middle line:84%
That as more and more people
are coming into an intention

00:39:08.890 --> 00:39:11.400 align:middle line:84%
to grow, develop,
and unfold, then,

00:39:11.400 --> 00:39:16.240 align:middle line:84%
the world changes and things,
systems that used to work,

00:39:16.240 --> 00:39:17.440 align:middle line:90%
no longer work.

00:39:17.440 --> 00:39:19.000 align:middle line:84%
Things that used
to be sustainable,

00:39:19.000 --> 00:39:20.571 align:middle line:90%
no longer sustainable.

00:39:20.571 --> 00:39:21.070 align:middle line:90%
You see?

00:39:21.070 --> 00:39:21.540 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:39:21.540 --> 00:39:23.581 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: So in that
third stage, we're saying,

00:39:23.581 --> 00:39:24.610 align:middle line:90%
what must we become.

00:39:24.610 --> 00:39:28.880 align:middle line:84%
And then, we ask what gifts
do we already have to share.

00:39:28.880 --> 00:39:30.880 align:middle line:84%
And then, we ask,
what must I let

00:39:30.880 --> 00:39:35.380 align:middle line:84%
go of that no longer
serves where I'm going?

00:39:35.380 --> 00:39:36.970 align:middle line:84%
All of these are
questions that allow

00:39:36.970 --> 00:39:39.390 align:middle line:84%
us to take the responsibility
for our own life.

00:39:39.390 --> 00:39:42.620 align:middle line:84%
And as you've indicated, when
people realize, oh, my God.

00:39:42.620 --> 00:39:43.846 align:middle line:90%
I've got to change.

00:39:43.846 --> 00:39:44.346 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:39:44.346 --> 00:39:44.700 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:39:44.700 --> 00:39:46.283 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: Or when
an issue comes up,

00:39:46.283 --> 00:39:49.630 align:middle line:84%
and they think, oh, it was a lot
better when I had problems when

00:39:49.630 --> 00:39:56.110 align:middle line:84%
I could anesthetize myself with
shopping, happy hour, whatever

00:39:56.110 --> 00:39:57.320 align:middle line:90%
the drug of choice is.

00:39:57.320 --> 00:39:59.320 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you could
never told me at that time

00:39:59.320 --> 00:40:01.980 align:middle line:84%
that I was attracting the bad
situations I was in because

00:40:01.980 --> 00:40:02.480 align:middle line:90%
of me.

00:40:02.480 --> 00:40:02.850 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Right.

00:40:02.850 --> 00:40:05.350 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Because I was attracting
the wrong business partner,

00:40:05.350 --> 00:40:08.709 align:middle line:84%
or I was attracting the
wrong set of circumstances.

00:40:08.709 --> 00:40:10.250 align:middle line:84%
You could have never
told me that was

00:40:10.250 --> 00:40:10.630 align:middle line:90%
me that was attracting that.

00:40:10.630 --> 00:40:11.338 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Yeah.

00:40:11.338 --> 00:40:13.460 align:middle line:90%
Because you weren't to blame.

00:40:13.460 --> 00:40:15.030 align:middle line:90%
Ignorance is always to blame.

00:40:15.030 --> 00:40:17.170 align:middle line:90%
It's never the individual.

00:40:17.170 --> 00:40:19.740 align:middle line:84%
It's just that an
individual doesn't know.

00:40:19.740 --> 00:40:22.280 align:middle line:84%
And so I look at those
particular things

00:40:22.280 --> 00:40:27.260 align:middle line:84%
as initiation, rather than
you made a horrible mistake.

00:40:27.260 --> 00:40:30.400 align:middle line:84%
Or if something bad
happened to you as a kid.

00:40:30.400 --> 00:40:33.800 align:middle line:84%
Those are points of initiations
where you get to learn

00:40:33.800 --> 00:40:36.520 align:middle line:84%
and activate certain
gifts within you,

00:40:36.520 --> 00:40:38.610 align:middle line:84%
certain talents,
certain strengths

00:40:38.610 --> 00:40:42.350 align:middle line:84%
that that particular condition
is bringing out of you.

00:40:42.350 --> 00:40:43.850 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I love
that, initiations.

00:40:43.850 --> 00:40:45.040 align:middle line:84%
That's a good way
of looking back.

00:40:45.040 --> 00:40:46.090 align:middle line:90%
And I'm able to look back now.

00:40:46.090 --> 00:40:48.090 align:middle line:84%
I have a different
perspective on all of it now.

00:40:48.090 --> 00:40:51.050 align:middle line:84%
And so this space
I'm in now is what

00:40:51.050 --> 00:40:54.790 align:middle line:90%
you call spiritual liberation.

00:40:54.790 --> 00:40:56.900 align:middle line:84%
This is what you
call that place where

00:40:56.900 --> 00:41:03.000 align:middle line:84%
I have freedom to be really
truly authentically who I am.

00:41:03.000 --> 00:41:06.260 align:middle line:84%
And not afraid of it,
not preachy about it,

00:41:06.260 --> 00:41:07.410 align:middle line:90%
but just to be it.

00:41:07.410 --> 00:41:08.170 align:middle line:90%
>>BECKWITH: Right.

00:41:08.170 --> 00:41:12.830 align:middle line:84%
You're not-- when you start
to touch spiritual liberation,

00:41:12.830 --> 00:41:14.690 align:middle line:84%
you're not just
free from something.

00:41:14.690 --> 00:41:15.600 align:middle line:84%
In the beginning,
people are just

00:41:15.600 --> 00:41:17.016 align:middle line:84%
trying to get free
from something.

00:41:17.016 --> 00:41:18.770 align:middle line:90%
I want to get free from hate.

00:41:18.770 --> 00:41:21.160 align:middle line:90%
I want to get free from fear.

00:41:21.160 --> 00:41:22.860 align:middle line:90%
I want to get free from lack.

00:41:22.860 --> 00:41:24.710 align:middle line:84%
But as you begin
to grow, it's more

00:41:24.710 --> 00:41:27.160 align:middle line:90%
of a freedom to be something.

00:41:27.160 --> 00:41:30.120 align:middle line:84%
So it's a freedom to be
rather than freedom from.

00:41:30.120 --> 00:41:33.230 align:middle line:84%
And in spiritual liberation,
now your pulled by a vision.

00:41:33.230 --> 00:41:36.100 align:middle line:84%
One of the things that I
teach in spiritual liberation

00:41:36.100 --> 00:41:38.730 align:middle line:84%
and in life visioning
is that we're pulled.

00:41:38.730 --> 00:41:42.790 align:middle line:84%
We're pushed by pain until
we're pulled by a vision.

00:41:42.790 --> 00:41:46.590 align:middle line:84%
And so once liberation
starts to happen within you,

00:41:46.590 --> 00:41:48.350 align:middle line:84%
you start to be more
pulled by a vision

00:41:48.350 --> 00:41:49.836 align:middle line:90%
rather than pushed by pain.

00:41:49.836 --> 00:41:51.960 align:middle line:84%
So even though there still
maybe pain in your life,

00:41:51.960 --> 00:41:54.590 align:middle line:84%
the world of phenomena
is still doing its thing,

00:41:54.590 --> 00:41:56.840 align:middle line:84%
you're vision is what
wakes you up every morning.

00:41:56.840 --> 00:41:58.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's
where I see we are

00:41:58.240 --> 00:42:01.090 align:middle line:84%
at the culture is that there's
still the push by paint.

00:42:01.090 --> 00:42:03.200 align:middle line:84%
There's civil unrest
in the Middle East.

00:42:03.200 --> 00:42:04.470 align:middle line:90%
There's natural disasters.

00:42:04.470 --> 00:42:06.000 align:middle line:84%
There's devastation
all around us.

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:10.930 align:middle line:84%
But there's a vision that is
calling, that is in the future.

00:42:10.930 --> 00:42:13.540 align:middle line:84%
It's here, and we get
glimpses of it now.

00:42:13.540 --> 00:42:15.640 align:middle line:84%
But then, how do you
suggest that we do deal

00:42:15.640 --> 00:42:19.549 align:middle line:84%
with that civil unrest
and the bombings and--

00:42:19.549 --> 00:42:21.090 align:middle line:84%
>>BECKWITH: Well,
first of all, there

00:42:21.090 --> 00:42:27.470 align:middle line:84%
is-- that type of cantankerous
behavior is in the Middle East,

00:42:27.470 --> 00:42:29.220 align:middle line:84%
but it's also in other
parts of the world.

00:42:29.220 --> 00:42:32.970 align:middle line:84%
We focus-- that's where we
on focus all the time, what's

00:42:32.970 --> 00:42:37.635 align:middle line:84%
happening with Palestine and
Israel and the Middle East.

00:42:37.635 --> 00:42:39.010 align:middle line:84%
But we can go to
parts of Africa.

00:42:39.010 --> 00:42:40.170 align:middle line:90%
We can go to the Congo.

00:42:40.170 --> 00:42:42.400 align:middle line:84%
We can go all around
the world and find

00:42:42.400 --> 00:42:46.080 align:middle line:84%
very similar kind
of civil unrest.

00:42:46.080 --> 00:42:47.010 align:middle line:90%
So it's happening.

00:42:47.010 --> 00:42:50.330 align:middle line:84%
However, if you look back at
the arc of human civilization,

00:42:50.330 --> 00:42:53.480 align:middle line:84%
we have less wars on the planet
now than any time in history,

00:42:53.480 --> 00:42:55.980 align:middle line:84%
less war than any
time in human history.

00:42:55.980 --> 00:42:57.490 align:middle line:90%
So something has shifted.

00:42:57.490 --> 00:42:59.300 align:middle line:84%
So we're putting
a magnifying glass

