00:43:28.010 --> 00:43:29.900 align:middle line:90%
Where am I holding grudges?

00:43:29.900 --> 00:43:31.740 align:middle line:84%
Where am I lacking
compassion and not

00:43:31.740 --> 00:43:34.950 align:middle line:84%
